OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK energy bills to be cut  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fby hundreds as part of     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FÂ£10bn support package     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK households are set to have hundreds 
OL,6, of pounds knocked off energy bills this
OL,7, winter as part of a #10bn package to   
OL,8, help people cope with soaring prices.  
OL,10,FThe government had said people would   
OL,11,Fget #200 off bills from October, which 
OL,12,Fthey would pay back over five years.   
OL,14,FHowever, the BBC understands that sum  
OL,15,Fwill be increased, possibly doubled,   
OL,16,Fand will not need to be repaid.        
OL,18,FThe support, to be announced by the    
OL,19,Fchancellor on Thursday, is expected to 
OL,20,Fbe funded in part by a windfall tax.   
